    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endeavor Is A 3d Deep Space Adventure.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your purpose is to explore, investigate, gather, build and battle your way through the unknown frontiers of infinite space-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras/150794c1fbcfab962ad9ff8796bea8d2.avif?t=1741652796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras_big/150794c1fbcfab962ad9ff8796bea8d2.avif?t=1741652796 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore an infinite universe</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Traverse vast, procedurally generated galaxies teeming with undiscovered sectors of space.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Encounter diverse topologies from asteroid belts to solar systems and explore the planets, suns,  asteroids, and meteors of deep space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras/f35e695e7d66a4a9083dc40fecf2f072.avif?t=1741652796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras_big/f35e695e7d66a4a9083dc40fecf2f072.avif?t=1741652796 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gather resources </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mine valuable resources from planets, asteroids, and meteors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect rare materials to trade and build advanced items. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras/25909eb92e31edd04f4480fa2345ce6a.avif?t=1741652796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras_big/25909eb92e31edd04f4480fa2345ce6a.avif?t=1741652796 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ensure your survival</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your ship's systems, including life support, energy, shields, and weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Overcome unknown challenges as you traverse through deep space where all entities have gravitational pull.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras/bccf0afcedf9d2c59721c69332bf2115.avif?t=1741652796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras_big/bccf0afcedf9d2c59721c69332bf2115.avif?t=1741652796 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your adventure</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Engage in dynamic, real-time combat against hostile entities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose your own path as you journey through Deep Space. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras/0d62b20c9fcc3f99f0c65e73e7d58676.avif?t=1741652796\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008810/extras_big/0d62b20c9fcc3f99f0c65e73e7d58676.avif?t=1741652796 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endeavor offers a vast, immersive universe to explore, filled with challenges, discoveries, and opportunities to shape your future. With its deep gameplay mechanics, stunning visuals, and engaging narrative, Endeavor invites you to embark on an unforgettable journey through the cosmos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
